&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualify Leads:&lt;/strong&gt; Engage with potential customers to qualify leads, ensuring they&#39;re a good fit for our product based on their needs and challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales Collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;: Work closely with the sales team to transition qualified leads and ensure a seamless handover process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CRM Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Regularly update and maintain the CRM with accurate data, notes, and follow-up tasks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Feedback Loop:&lt;/strong&gt; Provide insights to the product and marketing teams based on feedback and trends observed from the leads.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Meet &amp;amp; Exceed Targets:&lt;/strong&gt; Consistently achieve or surpass monthly and quarterly targets for qualified leads and appointments set.&lt;/li&gt;
