&lt;li&gt;Have experience in a hybrid model (both outbound and inbound)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with Salesforce and &lt;a href=&quot;http://Outreach.io&quot;&gt;Outreach.io&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written and verbal communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to understand Fingerprint&#39;s product details and articulate its value proposition.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Preferred Qualifications:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Business, Marketing, or related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in a startup environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of the device identity or anti-fraud industry a plus&lt;/li&gt;
